ingress controller

deploy ingress / nginx-ingress from nginx helm chart

expose traffic from out side the cluster to the services inside the cluster

traffic routing is controlled by the rules define inside the ingress

ingress used for:

1. externally reachable URLs
2. Load Balanced traffic
3. Terminate SSL
4. Name Based virtual hosting


Nginx , HA porxy, Traefik  V2.0 , google ingress controller (based on nginx)

one public IP

authentication with user name and password,

enable https

auto genterated self sign certficate


genetrate RBAC roles for nginx / Traefik





